      "value": "<p>Choose two from the following. You can perform each of the chosen options with your bonus action, instead of your action: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Applying poison</li>\n<li>Dash</li>\n<li>Disengage</li>\n<li>Guard</li>\n<li>Help</li>\n<li>Hide</li>\n<li>Search</li>\n<li>Throwing grenades and setting mines</li>\n<li>While mounted on a controlled beast, having your beast make a single melee attack against a creature within its reach</li>\n<li>While mounted on a vehicle, taking a vehicle action (you can't take the same action twice in one turn)</li></ul>",
